cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DL, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with document image classification using deep learning architectures and transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses advanced training strategies and analyzes the impact of training data, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DL (Deep Learning). Finally, the paper uses two datasets, which could also fall under the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
